.TH "__cci_control_port_by_index" 9 "__cci_control_port_by_index" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
__cci_control_port_by_index \- function to control a CCI port by port index
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int notrace" __cci_control_port_by_index
.BI "(u32 port "  ","
.BI "bool enable "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "port" 12
port index previously retrieved with \fBcci_ace_get_port\fP
.IP "enable" 12
if true enables the port, if false disables it
.SH "RETURN"
0 on success
-ENODEV on port index out of range
-EPERM if operation carried out on an ACE PORT
